=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
היא -  הוּא / hû'  hîy' / hoo, he
=== Etymology ===

The second form is the feminine beyond the Pentateuch; 
=== Pronun ===
a primitive word, the third person pronoun singular, he (she or it); only expressed when emphatic or without a verb; also (intensively) self, or (especially with the article) the same; sometimes (as demonstrative) this or that; occasionally (instead of copula) as or are: - he, as for her, him (-self), it, the same, she (herself), such, that (. . . it), these, they, this, those, which (is), who.